OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781021474
OL,3,CGreen Party councillor slams 'false'
OL,4,Cclaims he praised October 7th and Hamas
OL,6,FA Green Party councillor has said
OL,7,Fallegations that called a proscribed
OL,8,Fterrorist group "courageous" and
OL,9,Fpraised the October 7th attacks on
OL,10,FIsrael are "false" and "a gross
OL,11,Fmisrepresentation".
OL,13,FCllr Kamel Hawwash was elected for the
OL,14,FGreen Party in the Stirchley ward of
OL,15,FBirmingham in May this year.
OL,17,FHe is Birmingham's first Palestinian
OL,18,Fcouncillor and has been an outspoken
OL,19,Fcritic of the Israeli Defence Force.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
