OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781021474
OL,3,CGreen Party councillor slams 'false'
OL,4,Cclaims he praised October 7th and Hamas
OL,6,FFollowing Cllr Hawwash's announcement
OL,7,Fas a Green candidate, it was widely
OL,8,Freported that he praised the October
OL,9,F7th attacks, describing them as
OL,10,F"courage in the face of aggression".
OL,12,FOn 7 October 2023, the Palestinian-
OL,13,Fbased terrorist group Hamas launched
OL,14,Fan attack on Israel, killing almost
OL,15,F1,200 people.
OL,17,FThe attack was the spark that led
OL,18,FIsrael to begin its large-scale
OL,19,Fmilitary operation in Gaza.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781021474
OL,3,CGreen Party councillor slams 'false'
OL,4,Cclaims he praised October 7th and Hamas
OL,6,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News
OL,7,FCentral, Mr Hawwash has said these
OL,8,Fallegations are "false" and condemned
OL,9,Fthe attacks on civilians.
OL,11,FHe says the comments have been
OL,12,Fmisattributed to him and instead came
OL,13,Ffrom the title of a news segment on a
OL,14,FLebanese news channel on which he
OL,15,Fappeared.
OL,17,FMr Hawwash said: "Suggesting that
OL,18,Fthese words were my own is a gross
OL,19,Fmisrepresentation."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
