SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781021474
OL,3,CGreen Party councillor slams 'false'
OL,4,Cclaims he praised October 7th and Hamas
OL,6,FCllr Hawwash has been appointed
OL,7,Fcabinet member for children, young
OL,8,Fpeople and families in the new Green,
OL,9,FLib Dem, Independent coalition.
OL,11,FHis appointment has led Jewish groups
OL,12,Fin Birmingham to call on the new
OL,13,Fcouncil leader, Roger Harmer, to
OL,14,Freconsider his appointment.
OL,16,FIn a letter to Cllr Harmer, Ruth
OL,17,FJacobs, chair of the Jewish
OL,18,FRepresentative Council of Birmingham
OL,19,Fand West Midlands, said Cllr Hawwash
OL,20,Fshouldn't be given any power within
OL,21,Fthe council.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781021474
OL,3,CGreen Party councillor slams 'false'
OL,4,Cclaims he praised October 7th and Hamas
OL,6,FShe also said promotion "to any
OL,7,Fposition in the council administration
OL,8,Fis totally unacceptable."
OL,10,FCllr Hawwash has also been criticised
OL,11,Ffor describing Zionism, support for
OL,12,Fthe existence of the state of Israel,
OL,13,Fas "Jewish supremacy".
OL,15,FHe previously left the Labour Party in
OL,16,F2023, accusing Sir Keir Starmer of
OL,17,F"blind support for Israel," before
OL,18,Fjoining the Greens.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
