PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781021474
OL,3,CGreen Party councillor slams 'false'
OL,4,Cclaims he praised October 7th and Hamas
OL,6,FMr Hawwash denies that he supports
OL,7,FHamas and "reject(s) claims of
OL,8,Fantisemitism".
OL,10,FIn the statement to ITV News Central,
OL,11,FCllr Hawwash said, "It is entirely
OL,12,Ffalse to claim that I praised the 7
OL,13,FOctober attacks or described them as
OL,14,F'courageous'.
OL,16,F"I shared a video from a major
OL,17,FLebanese news channel on which I
OL,18,Fappeared as an academic and political
OL,19,Fanalyst discussing events in Gaza on
OL,20,F17 October.
OL,26,@oD@RpmoD@Tpn
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781021474
OL,3,CGreen Party councillor slams 'false'
OL,4,Cclaims he praised October 7th and Hamas
OL,6,F"I was not discussing the events of 7
OL,7,FOctober, and I unequivocally condemn
OL,8,Fall attacks on civilians.
OL,10,F"The headline 'Special Coverage   10
OL,11,FDays of the Al-Aqsa Flood: Heroism in
OL,12,Fthe Face of Aggression' was the
OL,13,Fbroadcaster's title for the news
OL,14,Fsegment, not a statement by me.
OL,15,FSuggesting that these words were my
OL,16,Fown is a gross misrepresentation.
OL,26,@rD@aP~
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
