OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781021474
OL,3,CGreen Party councillor slams 'false'
OL,4,Cclaims he praised October 7th and Hamas
OL,6,F"I reject claims of antisemitism. I am
OL,7,Ffully committed to standing up for all
OL,8,FBirmingham's diverse communities and
OL,9,Fworking to ensure Birmingham is a
OL,10,Fwelcoming place for all of them.
OL,12,F"I am grateful for the support I have
OL,13,Fhad from a wide range of individuals
OL,14,Fand groups."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
